title: Narrative

Compares the standard interactive <<.def "tabs">> macro with `<<.def "static-tabs">>` in `sections` mode. Internal headings auto-demote via [[tv-adjust-heading-level Variable]].

+
title: Output

;Interactive tabs (default)

<<tabs "[[SampleTabOne]] [[SampleTabTwo]] [[SampleTabThree]] [[SampleTabFour]]" "SampleTabOne" "$:/state/test/static-tabs/outer">>

-----

;Explicit static-tabs, sections mode

<<static-tabs "[[SampleTabOne]] [[SampleTabTwo]] [[SampleTabThree]] [[SampleTabFour]]" "" "" "h2" "demo">>
